snippet.title: Amber Heard EXPOSED By Police Footage and Faces Prison!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard EXPOSED By Police Footage and Faces Prison!   
The domestic abuse scandal between Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard has been making headlines for roughly 3 years now. Up until now, all odds have been in favor of Amber Heard however, there are still some people out there that believe Johnny Depp is innocent of Ambers assault claims. And if the LAPD footage that is making rounds on social media is anything to go by, the group of people who supported Johnny from the beginning have been right all along, but we will let you be the judge of that. Today, we will be discussing the LAPD Footage that exposed Amber Heard.
